Interface ManagedMessage

    • Method Detail

      • createPacket

        byte[] createPacket()
        Creates a byte array representation of this message. This representation is used by the FlowManager to store and replay messages. Implementations should not cache this representation as it must reflect changes made to this message via setFlowId(Long) and setSplitHistory(SplitHistory). Implementations must be able to re-create native messages from this representation.
        Returns:
        a byte array representation of this message.
